{
  "name": "session-pilot",
  "version": "0.3.0",
  "description": "Windows-native multi-repo worktree dashboard with Claude session indicators (LIVE/idle/none), one-click claude --resume launch into a new Windows Terminal window, multi-key shift+click sort, virtual-scrolled table, full-message modal, parallel JSONL scan with SWR cache. Single port 8083. v0.3+ — no Zellij, no WSL.",
